Follow the steps to download Visual Studio 2019 and run the codes!

1. Download Visual Studio 2019 from the following line and follow the installation steps:
    https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/thank-you-downloading-visual-studio/?sku=Community&rel=16
    
2. Download the zip folder 'freeglut glew.zip' and put the following files into specified folders:
    i. All files in the include folder to be put in
        C:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Visual Studio\2019\Community\VC\Auxiliary\VS\include\gl
    
    ii. lib files - x64
        C:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Visual Studio\2019\Community\VC\Auxiliary\VS\lib\x64
        
    iii. lib files – win32    
        C:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Visual Studio\2019\Community\VC\Auxiliary\VS\lib\x86

    iv. dll files – win32
        C:\Windows\SysWOW64 
        
    v. dll files – x64
        C:\Windows\System32
    
3. Try and run your code.
